high_descs: Turn right, walk down the corridor, go a step left when passing a countertop.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Walk to the sofa that is behind you, go right inside a room with a bed and approach the bed corner with a bread on it.
Slice the bread with the knife.
Take a step aside to the right.

Pick up a bread slice from the bed.
Leave the room but walk straight until you reach the wall and then left until you reach the microwave.
Put the bread slice in the microwave, heat it up for a while, then take it out.
Move to the right where the fridge is.
Put the bread in the fridge.
